_more_ - display file contents page by page

_more_ [-*bcx*] [*name1*...]

 *-b*  display *\*text\** and *\_text\_* in the input as bold and underlined *text*
 *-c*  emit ANSI color sequences instead of bold and underlined text
 *-x*  display bold and underlined output as plain text

 *name1*...  files to show

The *COLUMNS* and *LINES* environment variables override the default terminal size.
